reviews.text: Family having a craving for bubble tea after a very late dim sum lunch.  Got the fix at this popular bubble tea shop at mongkok. Roasted oolong tea with milk and yam Pearls.  Nice interesting tea mixed with juices.  Tried both the pineapple as well as the grapefruit variants and they are very good.

Interesting concept of bubble tea as compared to other bubble tea outlets. You can actually see them grind the tea leaves and brew it almost immediately upon ordering. And you have the option to customise your drinks based on the types of milk, flavours as well as tea leaves.
Excellent brew-to-order tea concept. Fast and efficient service.
Great shop, excellent drinks, but very busy, so almost no place to sit and need to wait quite some time. But the waiting is worthwhile!
Delicious teas, huge variety and fast service. Bubble tea isn't my first choice, but when I have one I get it here

reviews.text: 由：人工色素,化學香精,人造糖精 制成既野都係少飲為妙
叫了杯無糖烏龍, 有點苦澀, 有點失望

好喝 茶味很足夠
而且可以有多種配搭
很適合喜歡嘗試不同口味的人
原葉茶也令不愛喝糖的我大開眼界
以為無糖茶大都一樣甘苦
原來也有不同的味道餘韻
茶機也很有趣 可以嘗試摸摸蒸氣
店周圍都有茶的味道
但座位很少
很多時被大媽霸佔就沒地方坐
星巴克的位置被多亦較明亮
求其叫了number one的，很好飲下次會再飲
